sentence: At  least  16  Palestinians  were  killed  in  the  strike,  Reuters  reported.
The  IDF  said  "a  number  of  terrorists"  were  killed  in  counterterrorism  operations;  Palestinian  health  officials  reported  at  least  11  deaths.
In  total,  at  least  80  people  in  the  West  Bank  have  been  killed  by  Israeli  forces  since  the  start  of  the  war  earlier  this  month,  according  to  Palestinian  officials.
